<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>The Rise of HoYoverse</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark bg-dark">
        <div class="container">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#">HoYoverse</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="bg-primary text-white text-center py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h1 class="display-4">The Rise of HoYoverse Games</h1>
            <p class="lead">
                How HoYoverse became one of the biggest names in modern gaming.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="container my-5">
        <h2>Introduction</h2>
        <p>
            HoYoverse has become one of the most influential game developers
            in the world. Through high-quality visuals, engaging stories,
            and free-to-play accessibility, their games have attracted
            millions of players worldwide.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Games Section -->
    <div class="container my-5">
        <div class="row">

            <!-- Genshin -->
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200"
                         class="card-img-top"
                         alt="Genshin Impact">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Genshin Impact (2020)</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            An open-world RPG that popularized HoYoverse globally.
                            Featuring the world of Teyvat, elemental combat,
                            and continuous content updates.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- HSR -->
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200"
                         class="card-img-top"
                         alt="Honkai Star Rail">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Honkai: Star Rail (2023)</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            A turn-based RPG set across the stars.
                            The game expanded HoYoverse's audience through
                            strategic combat and cinematic storytelling.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- ZZZ -->
            <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x200"
                         class="card-img-top"
                         alt="Zenless Zone Zero">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h3 class="card-title">Zenless Zone Zero (2024)</h3>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            A fast-paced urban action RPG featuring stylish
                            combat, unique characters, and a modern city setting.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Why Successful -->
    <section class="bg-light py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>Why HoYoverse Became Successful</h2>

            <ul class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    High-quality graphics and animation
                </li>

                <li class="list-group-item">
                    Free-to-play with cross-platform support
                </li>

                <li class="list-group-item">
                    Frequent updates and events
                </li>

                <li class="list-group-item">
                    Strong storytelling and world-building
                </li>

                <li class="list-group-item">
                    Large global community
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Conclusion -->
    <div class="container my-5">
        <h2>Conclusion</h2>

        <p>
            From Genshin Impact's explosive launch to the success of
            Honkai: Star Rail and Zenless Zone Zero, HoYoverse has
            established itself as a major force in the gaming industry.
            Their commitment to quality and continuous innovation
            has helped them build one of the most dedicated gaming
            communities in the world.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center p-3">
        <p>Created using Bootstrap 5</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
